# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Test + coverage output
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Raw live community code pulled by `pnpm parity:bakery` (20-15 V-1).
# Never vendored — it is unreviewed third-party source; only the dated
# `result-*.json` % is transcribed by hand into the phase SUMMARY, and
# the 6 reviewed bakery-*.strudel fixtures are the tracked CI floor.
packages/app/tests/parity-corpus/.bakery-runs/
test-results/
packages/**/test-results/
playwright-report/
coverage/
.nyc_output/

